Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: word n. brown
des: This a simple skill to learn about the Word and Brown Companies and services it provides for brokers, employers, employees. You can ask general questions about the company such as, where is the nearest Word and Brown office, or why would I choose to work with Word and Brown? This skill is still new and more information will be added overtime as the skill grows. If you have any further questions that are not answered in the skill, you can always visit www.wordandbrown.com
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
